	<description>
		<![CDATA[
		<div align="center">
			<div class="alert alert-success" style="background-color:#DFF0D8;border-color:#D6E9C6;color: #468847;padding: 1px 0;">
				<h3><a href="http://www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-rent">Responsive Joomla template for Car Rental | JA Rent</a></h3>
				<h4><a href="http://ja-rent.demo.joomlart.com/" title="">Demo</a> | <a href="http://www.joomlart.com/documentation/joomla-templates/ja-rent" title="">Document</a> | <a href="http://pm.joomlart.com/browse/JATCRENT" title="">Changelog</a></h4>
				<p>JA Rent is Joomla template designed for Vehicle rental service website. The template is fully responsive based on Bootstrap 3 grid system. It is built with our solid T3 Framework, supports K2 component and dedicated Car rental component - Vik Rent Car that gives you power to build a full Rental functionality website.</p>
				<p>The theme has its own control panel with a lot of options to manage and customize your site: Logo replacement, Megamenu builder, Visual layout configuration, ThemeMagic - a truly magic tool to customize your theme based on pre-defined parameters.</p>
				<p>JA Rent supports RTL language layouts.</p>
				<span style="color:#FF0000">Note: JA Rent requires T3 plugin to be installed and enabled.</span><p></p>
				<p>Copyright 2004 - 2015 <a href='http://www.joomlart.com/' title='Visit Joomlart.com!'>JoomlArt.com</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<style>table.adminform{width: 100%;}</style>
		</div>
		]]>
	</description>
